      <title>美联储发言人称市场为大数据周做准备，美国国债价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/treasuries-drop-as-market-braces-for-big-data-week-fed-speakers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国债价格周一下跌，因为交易员们等待本周大量的经济数据和美联储官员的讲话，这可能会决定本月晚些时候央行政策决定的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/treasuries-drop-as-market-braces-for-big-data-week-fed-speakers</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 14:27:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大众汽车约 66,000 名工人因削减成本而罢工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/vw-workers-start-walkouts-over-plans-to-slash-costs-in-germany</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，德国各地约有 66,000 名大众汽车公司工人辞职，这是因如何削减该汽车制造商同名品牌的成本僵局而引发的第一波临时罢工。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/vw-workers-start-walkouts-over-plans-to-slash-costs-in-germany</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 09:02:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
